gomodel:SYNGO_2132  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.1: \"In nerve terminals, the matrix of LDCVs was, in general, strongly\nlabeled by antibodies to SgII\"\n\nFig.2: \"In neuritic processes, labeled LDCVs were also often observed.\nIn contrast to axon terminals, no other membranous structures such\nas axonal reticulum, vacuoles, or multivesicular bodies were labeled\n(Figure 2).\". Experimental description: \"Mouse hypothalami taken from fetuses on Day 15 of gestation were....\"" ;
